Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBInterfaceLog

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBInterfaceLog
public class JDBInterfaceLog
extends java.lang.Object
JDBInterfaceLog is used to record all activities of the interface module. The data is stored in the table SYS_INTERFACE_LOG When a messages is processed, whether it be inbound or outbound its recorded in this log along with the status, Success or Fail. A screen within the application allows messages to be re-processed if needed.

See Also:
JDBInterfaceRequest
